reviewText: Great product.  Unfortonately has no portuguese (or other) subtitles. Could be region free, also (Region1). Package content arrived ok with all disks; supports intact..
Excelent quality, the product bring good aditional material and a good presentation, a series to enjoy a pleasant. Great product for this series fans or collectors.

Excelente, es la serie que estaba buscando y llego bastante rapido, habia buscado esta serie por varios estados de Mexico y la encontre a buen precio y exactamente la que estaba buscando. Recomiendo apliamente al proveedor.
